post_title: WTB: Help me finish my Rare Back HOF Set
post_content:
Hey all, 

Looking a nice examples of the below.  Thanks for any leads or interest! 

Bender (No Trees) - Tolstoi, EPDG or Lenox
Bresnahan (Portrait) - EPDG, Old Mill or Hindu
Brown (Cubs on Shirt) - Hindu
Griffith (Portrait) - EPDG, Old Mill or Hindu
Jennings (Portrait) - EPDG or Old Mill
[STRIKE]Lajoie (Throwing) - EPDG, Old Mill or Hindu[/STRIKE]
Tinker (Hands on Knees) - Old Mill or Hindu

Also looking for Marquard (Follow Through) Lenox.  I have a Cycle 460 but am interested in the Lenox. 

Thanks - Kyle
Hey Kyle, good luck with the search.  Brown Cubs wasn't printed with Old Mill.  Just Hindu and Sov150 for tough backs on that one.

Was able to cross one off the list, updated original post above. 

Also, I am willing to let go of a few of these offback non-HOF available in the link below to pay for my unexpected sins at Heritage this past weekend. 

If interested, shoot me a message or reach out on instagram (in footer).
